recipesJson.name: Blue Kiwapple (a clone of "Keen", by Classified E-Liquids)
recipesJson.author: SumOldCant
recipesJson.description:
This is version 5 of a clone I've been working on, and i think it's at least a 90% match to the original.
It's a light juice, well balanced IMO, sometimes you get blueberry, sometimes kiwi/apple. Tastes a little creamy to me as well. My ADV.
All versions and full notes here on ELR.
http://e-liquid-recipes.com/recipe/758551/Classified+%2522KEEN%2522+Clone+V5
